<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>회원 가입</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@4.6.1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css">

    <style>
        .gradient-custom {
            background: linear-gradient(to right, rgba(254, 238, 229, 1), rgba(229, 193, 197, 1))
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="gradient-custom">
<section class="d-flex vh-100">
    <div class="container-fluid row justify-content-center align-content-center">
        <div class="card bg-dark" style="border-radius: 1rem;">
            <div class="card-body p-5 text-center">
                <h2 class="text-white">SIGN UP</h2>
                <p class="text-white-50 mt-2 mb-5">서비스 사용을 위한 회원 가입</p>

                <div class="mb-2">
                    <form action="/user" method="POST">
                        {{#_csrf}}
                            <input type="hidden" name="{{parameterName}}" value="{{token}}" />
                        {{/_csrf}}

                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label text-white">아이디</label>
                            <input type="id" class="form-control" name="id" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label text-white">비밀번호</label>
                            <input type="password" class="form-control" name="password" required>
                        </div>
                        <div class="mb-3">
                            <label class="form-label text-white">이름</label>
                            <input type="name" class="form-control" name="name" required>
                        </div>

                        <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary">회원가입 완료</button>
                    </form>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
</body>
</html>
